    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2008-07-30</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2008-10-27T16:50:19Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Fallen Hero Commemoration Act - Directs the Secretary of Defense to grant access to accredited members of the media: (1) at military commemoration ceremonies and military memorial services for members of the Armed Forces who have died on active duty; and (2) when the remains of such members arrive at U.S. military installations.</p> <p>Authorizes the Secretary to establish the policy for media accreditation.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Fallen Hero Commemoration Act</title>
