        <title>Fallen Hero Commemoration Act</title>
      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To require the Department of Defense to grant access to accredited members of the media at military commemoration ceremonies and memorial services for members of the Armed Forces who have died on active duty and when the remains of members of the Armed Forces arrive at military installations in the United States.</title>
      </item>
